“SAKAL BAN” – A tribute to devotion, music, and tradition. 🌼🎶

Experience the live rendition of this timeless qawwali by Mehfil-e-Sama’a, capturing the essence of Amir Khusrau’s offering to Hazrat Nizamuddin Aulia. 💛✨

With Irfan Erooth’s bold vocals, Jawed Aslam’s harmonium, Sikkani’s rhythmic magic on Tabla, and the soulful choir of Mehfil-e-Sama’a, this performance is pure spiritual bliss.

Now streaming everywhere! 🎧
